I write this message on behalf of the Proprietor of  
Fiji Eco Tours, Mr Michael Crocker:
The link mentioned advertises that a hacker has managed to hack into my  
site.  I think this is highly inappropriate content to be pasted onto  
google and should be removed.  This is affecting my business that I have  

operated for the last 13 years.  The link appears in a search result for
my  
domain "fijiecotours.net".  We have since rectified the hacking incident  

but the link still appears in the search result.
